description: This skill returns a fact about hockey. There are no hardware or account requirements. Users can prompt Alexa by saying "Alexa ask hockey stats". You then can ask Alexa for a fact by saying "give me a hockey fact" or "give me hockey trivia".
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask hockey stats to give me a hockey fact
Alexa ask hockey stats to tell me a hockey fact
name: Hockey Stats
shortDescription: This Alexa Skill returns a fact about hockey
